title: Hour 3 - Luke Fickell
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Luke Fickell
description:
Dan talks with Cincinnati HC Luke Fickell on the status of his team as they attempt to make it back to the College Football Playoff. Dan discusses the art of trash talking and it's prominence among the all-time greats.
